title: NFL Week 4 Recap (Football 10/01)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by John Breech, Sean Wagner and Ryan Wilson to recap all the action from Week 4 of the NFL season, including the Steelers ugly loss on Sunday night, Mitchell Trubisky's big breakout game, the Titans incredible comeback over the Eagles, some interesting coaching decisions and much more.
